<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Pliny%27s_Natural_History" title="Pliny's Natural History" class="mw-redirect">Pliny's Natural History</a> xxxiv.18.</li>
